```python
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns

import warnings
warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')

from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split
from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler
from imblearn.over_sampling import SMOTE
from imblearn.over_sampling import ADASYN
from sklearn import metrics

from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
from sklearn.metrics import roc_auc_score
from sklearn.metrics import classification_report
```


```python
from tensorflow import keras
from tensorflow.keras import Sequential, activations, layers
from tensorflow.keras.layers import Flatten, Dense, Dropout, BatchNormalization
from tensorflow.keras.layers import Conv1D, MaxPool1D
from tensorflow.keras.optimizers import Adam
```


```python
data = pd.read_csv('./data/creditcard.csv')
```


```python
# 현재 Time의 단위는 초 -> min,max값의 차이가 너무 큼
# 따라서 Time을 Time_day, Time_hour, Time_min으로 나눔
timedelta = pd.to_timedelta(data['Time'], unit = 's')
data['Time_day'] = (timedelta.dt.components.days).astype(int)
data['Time_min'] = (timedelta.dt.components.minutes).astype(int)
data['Time_hour'] = (timedelta.dt.components.hours).astype(int)
```


```python
# Amount역시 min, max값의 차이가 크므로 처리가 필요
# log변환
data['Amount'] = np.log(data['Amount'] + 0.001)
print('최대 Amount값:', data['Amount'].max())
print('최소 Amount값:', data['Amount'].min())
```

<pre>
최대 Amount값: 10.153902281764749
최소 Amount값: -6.907755278982137
</pre>

```python
# time_day 데이터 삭제
data.drop('Time_day',axis = 1, inplace = True)
```


```python
# 훈련 데이터, 테스트 데이터 분리 (6:4)
x = data.drop(['Class', 'Time'], axis = 1)
y = data.Class
x_train, x_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(x, y, test_size = 0.4, 
                                                    shuffle = True, stratify = y, random_state = 220625)
```


```python
# 검증 데이터, 테스트 데이터 분리(5:5)
x_test, x_val, y_test, y_val = train_test_split(x_test, y_test, test_size = 0.5,
                                               shuffle = True, stratify = y_test, random_state = 220625)
```


```python
scaler = StandardScaler()
x_train = scaler.fit_transform(x_train)
x_val = scaler.transform(x_val)
x_test = scaler.transform(x_test)
```


```python
val_data = pd.DataFrame(data = x_val, columns = x.columns)
val_data['Class'] = y_val.values
test_data = pd.DataFrame(data = x_test, columns = x.columns)
test_data['Class'] = y_test.values
```


```python
val_data = val_data.to_csv('./data/val_data.csv', index = False)
test_data = test_data.to_csv('./data/test_data.csv', index = False)
```


```python
# smote
sm = SMOTE()
x_train_sm, y_train_sm = sm.fit_resample(x_train, y_train)
```


```python
# numpy변환
y_train_sm = pd.Series(y_train_sm)
y_train_sm = y_train_sm.to_numpy()

y_val = y_val.to_numpy()
y_test = y_test.to_numpy()
```


```python
# 3차원으로 변경
x_train_sm = x_train_sm.reshape(x_train_sm.shape[0], x_train_sm.shape[1], 1)
x_val = x_val.reshape(x_val.shape[0], x_val.shape[1], 1)
x_test = x_test.reshape(x_test.shape[0], x_test.shape[1], 1)
```


```python
# MaxPool 코드 추가 나머지 동일, 마찬가지로 epochs 늘릴 예정
epochs = 100
model1 = Sequential()
model1.add(Conv1D(32, 2, input_shape = x_train_sm[0].shape))
model1.add(BatchNormalization())
model1.add(layers.Activation(activations.relu))
model1.add(Dropout(0.2))
model1.add(MaxPool1D(2))

model1.add(Conv1D(64, 2))
model1.add(BatchNormalization())
model1.add(layers.Activation(activations.relu))
model1.add(Dropout(0.3))
model1.add(MaxPool1D(2))

model1.add(Conv1D(128, 2))
model1.add(BatchNormalization())
model1.add(layers.Activation(activations.relu))
model1.add(Dropout(0.4))
model1.add(MaxPool1D(2))

model1.add(Conv1D(256, 2))
model1.add(BatchNormalization())
model1.add(layers.Activation(activations.relu))
model1.add(Dropout(0.5))
model1.add(MaxPool1D(2))


model1.add(Flatten())
model1.add(Dense(256, activation='relu'))
model1.add(Dropout(0.5))

model1.add(Dense(1, activation='sigmoid'))
```

```python
model1.summary()
```

```python
# 정확도 검사 및 시각화
# maxpool 추가 cnn 모델이 정확도가 더 높음
# 실제 사용할 cnn 모델
adam = keras.optimizers.Adam(learning_rate = 0.0002)
checkpoint_cb = keras.callbacks.ModelCheckpoint(
    "./best-smote-cnn-model.h5",
    save_best_only = True
)
early_stopping_cb = keras.callbacks.EarlyStopping(
    patience = 3,
    restore_best_weights = True
)
model1.compile(optimizer = adam, loss = 'binary_crossentropy', metrics=['accuracy'])

history = model1.fit(x_train_sm, y_train_sm, 
                    epochs=epochs, validation_data = [x_val, y_val], 
                    verbose=1, callbacks = [checkpoint_cb, early_stopping_cb])
```

```python
def plot_learningCurve(history, epoch):
  # Plot training & validation accuracy values
  epoch_range = range(1, epoch+1)
  plt.plot(epoch_range, history.history['accuracy'])
  plt.plot(epoch_range, history.history['val_accuracy'])
  plt.title('Model accuracy')
  plt.ylabel('Accuracy')
  plt.xlabel('Epoch')
  plt.legend(['Train', 'Val'], loc='upper left')
  plt.show()

  # Plot training & validation loss values
  plt.plot(epoch_range, history.history['loss'])
  plt.plot(epoch_range, history.history['val_loss'])
  plt.title('Model loss')
  plt.ylabel('Loss')
  plt.xlabel('Epoch')
  plt.legend(['Train', 'Val'], loc='upper left')
  plt.show()
```

```python
# cnn모델(구성은 동일)
epochs = 100
model3 = Sequential()
model3.add(Conv1D(32, 2, input_shape = x_train_gan[0].shape))
model3.add(BatchNormalization())
model3.add(layers.Activation(activations.relu))
model3.add(Dropout(0.2))
model3.add(MaxPool1D(2))

model3.add(Conv1D(64, 2))
model3.add(BatchNormalization())
model3.add(layers.Activation(activations.relu))
model3.add(Dropout(0.3))
model3.add(MaxPool1D(2))

model3.add(Conv1D(128, 2))
model3.add(BatchNormalization())
model3.add(layers.Activation(activations.relu))
model3.add(Dropout(0.4))
model3.add(MaxPool1D(2))

model3.add(Conv1D(256, 2))
model3.add(BatchNormalization())
model3.add(layers.Activation(activations.relu))
model3.add(Dropout(0.5))
model3.add(MaxPool1D(2))


model3.add(Flatten())
model3.add(Dense(256, activation='relu'))
model3.add(Dropout(0.5))

model3.add(Dense(1, activation='sigmoid'))
```


```python
adam = keras.optimizers.Adam(learning_rate = 0.0002)
checkpoint_cb = keras.callbacks.ModelCheckpoint(
    "./best-gan-cnn-model.h5",
    save_best_only = True
)
early_stopping_cb = keras.callbacks.EarlyStopping(
    patience = 3,
    restore_best_weights = True
)
model3.compile(optimizer = adam, loss = 'binary_crossentropy', metrics=['accuracy'])

history = model3.fit(x_train_gan, y_train_gan, 
                    epochs=epochs, validation_data = [x_val, y_val], 
                    verbose=1, callbacks = [checkpoint_cb, early_stopping_cb])
```
